items.badge_description: The battle for grid iron supremacy is on. Who will be the victor? Who are we kidding, with your favorite brew and this badge, you've already won!
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 130 distinct venues!

Whether you’re having a room party or hanging at the hotel bar, you know the essential part of any trip, an awesome beer!

That's a beer at 25 different venues categorized as a Hotel! Visit 5 more different ones for Level 6!
You're exploring this great country the best way possible, one delicious beer at a time! That's one beer while in at least 5 states or countries.
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 15 distinct venues!
Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 40 distinct venues!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 15 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 4!
Does the word picking favorites mean anything to you? Obviously not. That's 10 different beers in a row.

You're exploring this great country the best way possible, one delicious beer at a time! That's one beer while in at least 30 states or countries. Visit 5 more for Level 7!

Let the safari begin as your tastebuds take a tour of beers from the breweries of Africa. With nearly every country boasting it’s own brewery and a local favorites, there’s plenty to try. That's 5 different beers from a brewery located in the continent of Africa. Try 5 more for Level 2!
Travel much? You must be a "brewsetter". That's at least a beer from 20 different countries. Try 5 more for Level 5!
